{"article_id":"GJk9L0Yg5MX3vkGb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Former Gov . Mark Sanford ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"disgraced by affair ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"seeks old congressional seat","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"DeMint 's resignation triggered events","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that resulted in open seat in Congress","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Sanford is n't only distraction in race","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"--","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Ted Turner 's son is one of Sanford 's rivals","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Whichever of 16 candidates wins GOP race","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"will likely face sister of Stephen Colbert","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"after the former governor of the state infamously told the public","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"he was hiking the Appalachian Trail","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"while he was actually traveling to Argentina","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"to carry on an extramarital affair ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"a reintroduction would n't hurt .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"`` At some level or another we all hope for redemption , ''","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Sanford told CNN in an interview .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Sanford is one of 16 Republican candidates","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"seeking to win an open seat in South Carolina 's 1st Congressional District .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"It 's the same seat","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Sanford once held","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"before he ran for governor .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"An opportunity","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"to go to Washington","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"opened up in December","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"when Republican Rep. Tim Scott was appointed","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to replace outgoing Sen. Jim DeMint .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"With a bitter divorce from his wife , Jenny , now behind him ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Sanford is asking the public for a second chance .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"In his own informal poll of the voters , he 's finding an openness","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"to forgive ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"if not forget .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"`` What I would say on the larger notion of forgiveness is that some people forgave me the next day .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Some people will never forgive me , ''","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Sanford said .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Sanford 's colorful not so distant past is far from the only distraction in the race .","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Colbert talks sister 's run for Congress","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Colbert talks sister 's run for Congress","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"02:00","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Mark Sanford :","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"How I learned from scandal","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Mark Sanford :","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"How I learned from scandal","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"04:51","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"One of Sanford 's GOP rivals , Teddy Turner is the son of CNN founder Ted Turner .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"His family ties , deep pockets and sudden rise in some internal polling have made him a big target .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Opponents are filling mailboxes with attack ads on Turner ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"with some tying the candidate to one of his father 's ex-wives , Jane Fonda .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"`` You know","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"it 's absolutely amazing how dirty the game is ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"how expensive the game is .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"It just does n't make sense , ''","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Turner said .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"If that 's not enough","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"to grab the voters ' attention ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"the winner of Tuesday 's Republican primary will likely face the Democratic favorite , Elizabeth Colbert Busch .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Her brother just so happens to be Stephen Colbert , the host of Comedy Central 's `` Colbert Report .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"'' Only she pronounces Colbert with a hard `` T. ''","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Colbert Busch insists","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"her candidacy is no laughing matter .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"`` This is not a joke .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"I do n't think","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"anybody would think","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"that this was a joke .","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"This is all too important .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"All too important with the condition","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"that the country is in , ''","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"Colbert Busch told CNN .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"Many of the other candidates in the race also deserve to be taken seriously .","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"One potential spoiler on the Republican side is State Sen. Larry Grooms .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"He has collected some important local endorsements","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"and boasts a staff","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"that includes Hogan Gidley , a former spokesman for Rick Santorum , a former senator and Republican presidential candidate in 2012 .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"But with such a short election schedule and a Star Wars bar full of candidates , the race could turn on name recognition .","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"Translation :","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"advantage Sanford .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"John Avlon , a CNN political contributor","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"whose family has lived in South Carolina for decades ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Sanford 's honesty about his imperfect personal life has made him more relatable to voters .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"`` There is an affection for a guy","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"who admits","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"he 's a sinner","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"and asks for forgiveness , especially down here , ''","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"Avlon said .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"Despite his transgressions ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"the former governor insists","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"he is worthy of the public trust .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Sanford maintains","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"he learned some important life lessons","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"after wondering off-trail .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"`` Oddly enough , I think","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"you learn from the valleys of life rather than the peaks , ''","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Sanford said .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":203,"left":0,"right":202,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":109,"right":201,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":109,"left":106,"right":108,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":104,"right":105,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":103,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":6,"right":107,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":201,"left":137,"right":200,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":118,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":110,"right":117,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":110,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":117,"left":115,"right":116,"relation":"elabor